19th July 2015 ITV4
19:00 to 20:00 Stage 15 Highlights

Stage 15 is in theory one for the sprinters. The peloton descend from Mende down into the Rhone valley, climbing the cat two Col de l'Escrinet before a flat 30km to the finish in Valence. Presented by Gary Imlach with analysis from Chris Boardman, commentary from Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen with Ned Boulting reporting at the roadside.
